longBusinessSummary: Dacian Gold Limited engages in the exploration, mining, and processing of gold properties in Australia. It primarily focuses on its 100% owned Mount Morgans Gold project located near Laverton, Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is based in Como, Australia.
